keel.Algorithms.Subgroup_Discovery.SDIGA.SDIGA

Class CromCAN

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Subgroup_Discovery.SDIGA.SDIGA.CromCAN

  • public class CromCAN
extends java.lang.Object

    Defines the structure and manage the contents of a canonical rule. This implementation uses only integer values to store the gens.

    Since:
    JDK1.5

    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
